/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/jruj3vrmiovu4qqfeyt2 540w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/ypaoqcfmjolua07qoqz7 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/c8ia3q3eesvhtwuw9mx2 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/gar0odiju7riejkhuhmq 810w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/bzyi3inpj535lpzwxehk 890w"></figure><p>喜欢绿线胜过黄色宝石的特工通常也是喜欢绿线胜过红线的特工。但这并不是故事的全部，特别是当你考虑像最接近右下角的那个特工时 - 它的偏好是绿线而不是红线而不是黄色宝石。</p><h2>音乐隐喻</h2><p>音乐就是一个很好的比喻来说明这一点，我们所说的“声音”是 20 到 20,000 Hz 之间的波，而可见光是 400 到 700 THz 之间的波。如果同时在钢琴上弹奏音符C和E，人们会听到它们，而不是听到音符D。如果音符C代表红色，音符E代表绿色，则D将代表黄色。人类甚至无法区分单色黄色和由红色和绿色光线混合产生的黄色，而特工只将黄色视为红色和绿色。 </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:49.14%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/wyj9ej2cohs6yvxl6dv2" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/b8zazmnfomwixuwysh9q 110w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/kblvcymhg6lsd2kmdkel 220w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/vwgk72lfe9xh5gzkpbcf 330w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/n6miqqnuyrfvjqibzvyf 440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/oaoxhpyjx04aybuslgbi 550w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G5WjQZL5MqHftsh7D/ljhwmd856knpr0xsajqj 660w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/G